text: Colobothea viehmanni is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Monné and Martins in 1979. It is known to be from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Colobothea viehmanni. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1979
